{
  "name": "Athletics - Base",
  "type": "feat",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You have started to develop Athletics beyond other skills, delving deeper into its possibilities.</p><p><strong>Core Feats</strong></p><ul><li>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.feats-srd.Item.KxaYlC50zzHysJj8]{Titan Wrestler}</li></ul><p>Choose one Skill Path and gain that path's Trained feat.</p><p><strong>Available Skill Paths</strong></p><ul><li><strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-skillpaths.pf2e-skillpath-compendium.Item.DP9HZpKiMLumpv5N]{Jumping Path - Trained}</strong>: Thanks to your thorough training your jumping ability is extraordinary.</li><li><strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-skillpaths.pf2e-skillpath-compendium.Item.S7m5LJNHDLnOJtnu]{Climbing Path - Trained}</strong>: There are few people climbing as good as you do.</li><li><strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-skillpaths.pf2e-skillpath-compendium.Item.s33jZRlkY3uOvMpS]{Might Path - Trained}</strong>: As a martial artists you strive to master grappling and other hand to hand combat.</li><li><strong>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e-skillpaths.pf2e-skillpath-compendium.Item.iRAwxAGE0ppmefHX]{Swimming Path - Trained}</strong>: You focus on improving your swimming and diving, mastering the element of water.</li></ul>",
      "gm": ""
    },
